These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, april
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Birthday   | april | february |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
2 different games are played: snooker, scrabble
1. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
2. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Game   | snooker | scrabble |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
2 different pets are kept: frog, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Pet   | rabbit | frog |

 #################################

 
