.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, gospel
1. the fan of dubstep is on the far left##1
2. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |     2     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | gospel |

